***Code do compare the phenotype differences model to between family LPM results 
 
**load data
 clear all
 use "W:\Henrik\remake 120k 2025.dta"
 *drop none-genotyped individuals
 drop if sfm_PRS != 3
 
**coding of main variables is identical to sibling dataset

**the following lines show how variables used aditionally in the sample of unrelated individuals


*adding whether parents have ever been diagnoses with a mental illness
*alreadt in the data 
*merge m:1 m_shnro using "W:\Henrik\m_mental.dta", keep(match master) nogen 
*merge m:1 f_shnro using "W:\Henrik\f_mental.dta", keep(match master) nogen 
*gen p_mental = .
*replace p_mental = 0  if m_mental != .
*replace p_mental = 0  if f_mental != .
*replace p_mental = 1  if m_mental == 1
*replace p_mental = 1  if f_mental == 1

*label define  p_mental_label 0"No parental mental illness" 1"Parents had a mental health diagnosis" , replace
*label values  p_mental p_mental_label 


*Exclude individuals who died before age 14. And, those died before 1970 are not in the data 
gen ageatdeath = kuolv - syntyv
drop if ageatdeath < 14
*(0 observations deleted)

*Exclude those who were under 30 when inpatient hilmo started
drop if syntyv < 1940
*(7,431 observations deleted)

*Exclude those who were under average onset age when hilmo ended
drop if syntyv > 1995
*(30 observations deleted)

*age at last observation
gen age2020 = 2020 - syntyv 

*shorthen PGS to avoid error messages
rename SCZ_Ripke_2014_nofin_PRS_scaled  Schiz_PGS
rename Risk_taking_behaviour_PRS        Risk_PGS
rename EA_OkbayExclFinnGen_PRS_scaled   EA_PGS

*Produce GxE interactions product terms
    gen edu_bipo    = Bipolar_disorder_PRS * p_education
	gen edu_risk    = Risk_PGS * p_education
    gen edu_mood    = Mood_disorder_spectrum_PRS * p_education 
	gen edu_schiz   = Schiz_PGS * p_education 
	gen edu_depress = DEP6_PRS_scaled * p_education
	gen edu_neuro   = Neuroticism_PRS * p_education 
	gen edu_edu     = EA_PGS * p_education 
    gen edu_adhd    = ADHD_PRS * p_education
	
*Logarithmic version of total psychotropic medication costs in years
gen      medcostl = 1 if  years_psychotropicmed == .
replace  medcostl = years_psychotropicmed  if years_psychotropicmed != .
gen      lmedcost = log(medcostl)

*Combine psychotropic and schizzophrenia diagnoses to match original GWAS
gen     a1st_schizpsychotic = a1st_psychotic
replace a1st_schizpsychotic = a1st_schizophrenia  if a1st_schizophrenia < a1st_psychotic & a1st_schizophrenia !=.
tab     a1st_schizpsychotic
gen     schizpsychotic = 0 if a1st_schizpsychotic == .
replace schizpsychotic = 1 if a1st_schizpsychotic != .
tab     schizpsychotic
sum     schizpsychotic

*Define generation based on mother's year of birth
tab m_year_of_birth
gen generation = 0
replace generation = 1 if m_year_of_birth > 1933
label define generationl 0 "Old cohort" 1 "Young cohort" , replace
label values generation generationl
tab generation

*Prepare region of birth for analyses
destring smkunta, replace

*Outcomes
*This is to get prevalency, eg. for the relative increases 
summarize mental substance schizpsychotic antipsychotics_ever mood depressive antideps_ever bipolar anxiety anxiolytics_ever childbehav  adhd_ever 

*List of covariates
*female i.p_education  i.p_mental i.smkunta C1-C10
*Sex female = 1 
*Parental education high/more than basic education = 1
*Parental psychopathology combined
*Region of birth
*Top ten principal components




*add weights
merge 1:1 shnro using "W:\weight_project\Corrected_Weights\weights_prs.dta" , keep(match master) nogen 

sort  weights
gen   w_trim = weights
local low    = r(p1)
local high   = r(p99)

replace w_trim = max(`low', min(weights, `high'))
summarize w_trim, detail
gen w_final = w_trim / r(mean)
summarize w_final
*repeat all analyses appy weights




